  <div class="packet-section">
    <h3><span class="ps-icon">✅</span> Attendance &amp; Availability</h3>
    <p>{{ packet.attendance }}</p>
    <ul>
      <li>A minimum of <strong>24 hours' notice</strong> is required for any missed practice or game, except in cases of illness or emergency.</li>
      <li>Known conflicts must be communicated as soon as possible.</li>
      <li>Absences must be reported in the <strong>GameChanger app</strong> AND emailed to <a href="mailto:Staff@LawrenceHaymakers.com" style="color:var(--green);">Staff@LawrenceHaymakers.com</a>.</li>
      <li>Failure to communicate availability may affect playing time.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="packet-section">
    <h3><span class="ps-icon">⚾</span> Player Expectations</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Give consistent effort at practices and games.</li>
      <li>Be coachable and willing to learn.</li>
      <li>Show respect to teammates, coaches, opponents, and officials.</li>
      <li>Support teammates and put the team first.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="packet-section">
    <h3><span class="ps-icon">🤝</span> Parent Expectations &amp; Dugout Conduct</h3>
    <p>Parent conduct is non-negotiable. There is <strong>zero tolerance</strong> for negative reinforcement or disrespectful behavior during games or practices.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Encourage players positively — all players, not just your own.</li>
      <li>Allow coaches to coach. Do not coach from the stands.</li>
      <li>Address concerns privately with coaching staff.</li>
      <li><strong>Parents are not permitted in the dugout.</strong></li>
    </ul>
    <div class="highlight-box">
      <strong>Parent support is valued.</strong> We need help with dugout setup, scorekeeping, and stat tracking through GameChanger. Families interested in helping secure sponsorships are encouraged to reach out.
    </div>
  </div>

